            <bug_when>2009-01-18 02:53:58 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>The property highlightFocusRow was added at some point, in qx.ui.table.rowrenderer.Default. The row focus indicator could thus be be disabled with:

  table.getDataRowRenderer().setHighlightFocusRow(false);

For convenience, I&#39;ve now also added the ability to simply call:

  table.highlightFocusedRow(false)

Derrell
</thetext>
